sql:
SELECT name
FROM data_acquisition_systems
WHERE system_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- The query assumes that the version with the most recent creation date is the latest version of an experiment; 
- Data points are collected from various tables (encoder, adc, voltage, current, temperature) which might represent different types of data measured during the experiment; 
- The total number of data points collected might not necessarily reflect the quality or significance of the data, but rather the quantity.
